121

128 using Reply = std::tuple<std::optional<IPC::Attachment>&, WebCore::HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy&>;
129 using ReplyArguments = std::tuple<std::optional<IPC::Attachment>, WebCore::HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy>;
